{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":99,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":null,"text":"国先生确是豪气干云，只不知所说高人，指的是哪一位高人？","tone":"大笑","chapter":206,"line_start":18,"line_end":20},{"speaker":"char_guo_xing","speaker_name":"国兴","listener":"char_jing_jun","text":"国兴藉此良机，愿请荆副统领指教。","tone":"淡然","chapter":206,"line_start":22,"line_end":24},{"speaker":"char_ji_yan_ran","speaker_name":"纪嫣然","listener":null,"text":"不行！这场比试该是我的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":206,"line_start":28,"line_end":30},{"speaker":"char_guo_xing","speaker_name":"国兴","listener":"char_ji_yan_ran","text":"唉！纪才女身娇肉贵，小人怎敢冒犯不敬，更没有这个胆量，嘿！","tone":"无奈","chapter":206,"line_start":42,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_ji_yan_ran","speaker_name":"纪嫣然","listener":"char_guo_xing","text":"国先生请勿小觑我们女儿家，否则若吃大亏，莫怪嫣然没有预先警告。给我拿枪来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":206,"line_start":64,"line_end":66},{"speaker":"char_guo_xing","speaker_name":"国兴","listener":"char_ji_yan_ran","text":"这场算小人输了吧！国兴实无法兴起与才女动剑弄枪之念。","tone":"无奈","chapter":206,"line_start":70,"line_end":72}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_ji_yan_ran","name":"纪嫣然","alias":["纪才女"],"identity":"与琴清并称的才女，项少龙之妻","faction":null,"role":"companion","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"以琴艺武技冠绝当代的才女，项少龙之妻，枪法出神入化，特立独行。","personality":{"traits":["特立独行","艺高胆大","从容不迫","情操高尚","娇慵俏逸","聪慧果断"],"speech_style":"从容优雅，偶尔霸气","temperament":"沉稳自信"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"恋人","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"恩爱夫妻"},{"target":"char_guo_xing","type":"对手","intensity":30,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"比武较量"},{"target":"char_xiao_pan","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"受封太傅"}],"known_skills":["skill_fei_long_qiang_fa"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[206],"source_refs":[{"chapter":206,"line_start":34,"line_end":35,"text":"原来说此豪语者，竟是与琴清以色艺冠绝当代、美艳不可方物的才女纪嫣然。"},{"chapter":206,"line_start":54,"line_end":55,"text":"纪嫣然仍是那副娇慵倦懒的动人样儿，一点不像即赴战场的女武士"}]},{"id":"char_wu_guang","name":"乌光","alias":[],"identity":"项少龙手下，掌管飞龙枪","faction":null,"role":"companion","archetype":"warrior","rank":"初窥门径","one_line":"项少龙的忠心手下，负责掌管飞龙枪。","personality":{"traits":["忠心耿耿","恭敬","勤快","朴实","尽职尽责"],"speech_style":"恭敬","temperament":"沉稳"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"主仆","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"忠心下属"},{"target":"char_ji_yan_ran","type":"主仆","intensity":50,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"敬奉主母"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[206],"source_refs":[{"chapter":206,"line_start":68,"line_end":69,"text":"负责掌管飞龙枪的乌光，连忙解囊取枪，忙个不停。"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_wei_nan_wu_shi_xing_guan","name":"渭南武士行馆","type":"武林门派","location":"秦国","sub_divisions":[],"one_line":"秦国本土武术势力，以邱日升为首，依附嫪毐，与秦军方关系密切。","source_refs":[{"chapter":206,"line_start":2,"line_end":2,"text":"在嫪党之中，以邱日升为首的渭南武士行馆中人"}]}],"locations":[],"items":[{"id":"item_fei_long_qiang","name":"飞龙枪","type":"weapon","owner":"char_ji_yan_ran","one_line":"纪嫣然的全钢长枪，分量沉重，不易被削断。","description":"罕有的全钢长枪，没有木杆枪刚柔兼备的特性，分量沉重多了，更不虞会被削断，飙刺时速度特快，占本身重量便宜，力道非一般木杆枪可比。","effects":[],"origin":null,"rarity":"稀世珍品","related_characters":["char_ji_yan_ran","char_wu_guang"],"related_skills":["skill_fei_long_qiang_fa"],"rag_refs":[206],"source_refs":[{"chapter":206,"line_start":180,"line_end":181,"text":"纪嫣然这把飞龙枪，与一般长枪的最大分别是罕有的全钢枪，没有木杆枪刚柔兼备的特性，分量沉重多了"}]}]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_guo_xing","updates":{"one_line":"渭南武士行馆著名剑手，挑战荆俊，被纪嫣然击败后封都骑第三副统领。","personality":{"traits":["谦虚知礼","能屈能伸","感恩知报","武艺不凡","顾全大局"],"speech_style":"谦恭有礼","temperament":"沉稳"},"source_refs":[{"chapter":206,"line_start":22,"line_end":24,"text":"国兴藉此良机，愿请荆副统领指教。"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"add","target":"char_ji_yan_ran","type":"对手","intensity":30,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"比武败北"}]},{"id":"char_qiu_ri_sheng","updates":{"personality":{"traits":["阴险","傲慢","记仇","不甘失败","野心勃勃"],"speech_style":"阴沉","temperament":"冷酷"},"source_refs":[{"chapter":206,"line_start":2,"line_end":2,"text":"以邱日升为首的渭南武士行馆中人"}]},"relationship_update