{"segment":2,"line_start":100,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_guo_xing","text":"国先生搦战在先，现在有人应战，自不许临阵退缩。为免国先生故意落败，若先生挡不了这十枪，国先生将永不被寡人录用，国先生好自为之。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":206,"line_start":100,"line_end":104},{"speaker":"char_guo_xing","speaker_name":"国兴","listener":"char_ji_yan_ran","text":"嫣然小姐请赐教。","tone":"陈述","chapter":206,"line_start":118,"line_end":120},{"speaker":"char_ji_yan_ran","speaker_name":"纪嫣然","listener":"char_guo_xing","text":"嫣然这十枪只攻先生手中之剑，保证不会伤及先生身体，先生可抛开所有顾虑，全力防守。","tone":"淡然","chapter":206,"line_start":122,"line_end":124},{"speaker":"char_guo_xing","speaker_name":"国兴","listener":"char_ji_yan_ran","text":"请小姐赐教！","tone":"陈述","chapter":206,"line_start":142,"line_end":144}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[{"id":"skill_fei_long_qiang_fa","name":"飞龙枪法","type":"枪法","faction":null,"rank":"出神入化","one_line":"纪嫣然的家传枪法，以飞龙枪施展，灵活多变，虚实相生。","techniques":[{"id":"tech_qiang_ying_ji","name":"枪影击","type":"attack","description":"先扬枪洒出一片枪影，再收窄枪圈，滚滚枪影在身周烟花般烁动，令对手难辨虚实。"},{"id":"tech_xuan_zhuan_heng_sao","name":"旋转横扫","type":"attack","description":"枪杆紧贴腰身，身子急旋，藉转动之力将飞龙枪由直刺变成横扫，取对手剑鞘而非身体。"}],"progression":[],"effects":[],"combat_style":"以飞龙枪的重量和速度优势，配合灵活步法和腰马之力，虚实结合，攻敌必救之处。","rag_refs":[206],"source_refs":[{"chapter":206,"line_start":74,"line_end":75,"text":"纪嫣然一把接过乌光跪献的飞龙枪，先不理国兴，扬枪洒出一片枪影，再收窄枪圈，登时滚滚枪影"},{"chapter":206,"line_start":214,"line_end":215,"text":"枪杆变得紧贴腰身的一刻，身子急旋，藉转动之力，飞龙枪由直刺变成横扫"}]}],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_jing_jun","updates":{"personality":{"traits":["冲动好胜","服从指挥","重情重义","乐观开朗","年轻气盛"],"speech_style":"爽快直接","temperament":"活泼"},"source_refs":[{"chapter":206,"line_start":28,"line_end":29,"text":"荆俊先是呆了一呆，接着喜上眉梢"}]}},{"id":"char_teng_yi","updates":{"personality":{"traits":["沉稳","谨慎","有决断力","护持兄弟","冷静理智"],"speech_style":"低沉稳重","temperament":"沉稳"},"source_refs":[{"chapter":206,"line_start":40,"line_end":41,"text":"荆俊自不能让嫂子冒险，欲反对时，却给旁边的滕翼制止。"}]}},{"id":"char_lv_niang_rong","updates":{"personality":{"traits":["内心矛盾","情感纠结","犹豫不决","渴望关注","柔弱多情"],"speech_style":"含蓄内敛","temperament":"犹豫"},"source_refs":[{"chapter":206,"line_start":164,"line_end":169,"text":"吕娘蓉芳心抖颤，想起或者就是这只手把项少龙杀死"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"add","target":"char_guan_zhong_xie","type":"恋人","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"握手示情"},{"action":"add","target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"对手","intensity":40,"bond_level":1,"dynamic":"暗生情愫又矛盾"}]}]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":201,"line_end":288,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ji_yan_ran","speaker_name":"纪嫣然","listener":"char_guo_xing","text":"嫣然攻了五枪，先生挡过五枪，而嫣然之所以能着着领先，皆因先生遵诺只守不攻，不若就此作罢，算我们不分胜负。","tone":"微笑","chapter":206,"line_start":260,"line_end":262},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_ji_yan_ran","text":"好一位纪才女，谁能不心悦诚服，由今天开始，才女就是寡人的太傅。","tone":"大笑","chapter":206,"line_start":264,"line_end":266},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_guo_xing","text":"国先生能紧守寡人之命，只守不攻，亦是难得，就赐你为都骑第三副统领之职，归项统领管辖。","tone":"陈述","chapter":206,"line_start":268,"line_end":270},{"speaker":"char_lv_bu_wei","speaker_name":"吕不韦","listener":null,"text":"怕该是主菜上席的时候了。","tone":"大笑","chapter":206,"line_start":284,"line_end":286}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_pu_hu","name":"蒲鶮","alias":[],"identity":"嫪毐门下客卿，与杜璧同席","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"嫪毐门下客卿，好色之徒，垂涎纪嫣然美色。","personality":{"traits":["好色","善于逢迎","圆滑","爱出风头","见风使舵"],"speech_style":"油腔滑调","temperament":"轻浮"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_lao_ai","type":"主仆","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"门下客卿"},{"target":"char_du_bi","type":"合作者","intensity":30,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"同席"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[206],"source_refs":[{"chapter":206,"line_start":60,"line_end":61,"text":"他旁边的蒲鶮更是瞳仁差点瞪得掉下来，垂涎欲滴"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_guo_xing","updates":{"rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"渭南武士行馆著名剑手，被纪嫣然五枪击败后获封都骑第三副统领，归项少龙管辖。","source_refs":[{"chapter":206,"line_start":268,"line_end":270,"text":"就赐你为都骑第三副统领之职，归项统领管辖。"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"add","target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"主仆","intensity":50,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"归其管辖"},{"action":"add","target":"char_xiao_pan","type":"主仆","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"受封为臣"}]},{"id":"char_ji_yan_ran","updates":{"rank":"出神入化","one_line":"以琴艺武技冠绝当代的才女，项少龙之妻，枪法出神入化，被小盘